title: DAZ3D - On The Beach
description:
'On the beach' is a complete private beach for daytime scenes for DAZ Studio.

Most Mediterranean islands and coast have access to what is we call 'paillotes' in French. It's very different than a resort private beach. These paillotes are on the small beach during summer, frequently the place is not easy to access and isolated. Most of them have a little restaurant or cafe.
